products.title: Unilux PVC Blackout Lilac Purple Roller Blind
products.metadescription: Unilux PVC Blackout Lilac Purple Roller Blind in Purple. Made to measure from £10.04 with FREE UK mainland delivery. This Roller Blind includes 5-year guarantee and child safety features.
products.productdescription:
Give your bathroom or kitchen a modern makeover with the Unilux PVC Blackout Roller Blind. This roller blind is made from moisture resistant PVC and is guaranteed to give your space a fresh feel thanks to its contemporary design and crisp white finish. In addition, the blackout material will provide the required peace and privacy.
